{{Top}}
A '''cow''' was a [[species]] of creature that could be [[milk]]ed, similar to a [[nerf]].<ref name="SYWtBaJ">''[[The Empire Strikes Back: So You Want to Be a Jedi?]]''</ref> [[Kaadu]] resembled tall [[Limb|two-legged]] cows.<ref name="Creatures Big & Small">''[[Star Wars: Creatures Big & Small]]''</ref> On some occasions when [[Chef]] [[Strono Tuggs]] stationed his [[Tuggs' Grub|traveling restaurant]] at [[Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo]] in [[Batuu]]'s [[Black Spire Outpost]], he served [[Batuuan Beef Pot Roast]] produced by Batuuan cows that grazed [[Naboo]]'s grasslands.<ref name="Traveler's Guide">''[[Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge: Traveler's Guide to Batuu]]''</ref>

